entries.journal_entry_description: You're doing some entertainer work for Gendra.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go to the cantina and do the job that Gendra needs you to do.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Gendra asked you to fill in at the cantina again, this time for a musician who was arrested at the star port. Just go in and do 30 seconds of music, then return to Gendra.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You've finished playing at the Cantina. Now go see Gendra.
